---
title: Vegan Smoky BBQ Mushroom Sloppy Joes with Cilantro Lime Slaw, Potato Wedges & Hot Sauce
description: Our talented chefs work overtime to bring you the tastiest vegan recipes, and this one is a true gem. Earthy spiced mushrooms star in this plant-based spin on Sloppy Joes, with a supporting role going to caramelized onion draped in a tangy-sweet barbecue sauce. It’s all tucked together into a crusty baguette with lime-cilantro slaw for fresh, crunchy contrast (and as much hot sauce as you like). A side of crispy golden potato wedges rounds out this wholesome, colorful vegan dinner idea.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/vegan-smoky-bbq-mushroom-sloppy-joes-728805b7.jpg
